{"tid":388102,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"藍牙耳機2揀1","createTime":"2017-09-05T08:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T11:07:44.000Z","uid":137713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a86fa462fe95142a10669dab7ed881dd8e9aecb","tid":388102,"uid":137713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:03:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟之前用開個(垃圾)awei藍牙耳機壞左<br />\n所以想買過個<br />\n上網做完功課之後睇啱左2款<br />\n分別係Creative WP-250同BACKBEAT GO 3<br />\n我覺得兩個款各有好處<br />\nCreative WP-250就好在個mic係埋個耳機附近<br />\nBACKBEAT GO 3就好在有個充電袋同外表靚仔D<br />\n小弟對音質既要求唔高<br />\n只係希望個耳機D電襟用D<br />\n同埋收音唔好太差<br />\n各位可唔可以畀D意見小弟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外想問如何我用iphone<br />\n係咪無得用個藍牙耳機去較大細聲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1801878ce19676326c12c3954ceb8343d03acf44","tid":388102,"uid":137713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74db2751f6330947c86e5cce7297ca977524002d","tid":388102,"uid":137713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f98640c73427ed4f71c905cc5ab0ccf5857daea","tid":388102,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:2